  "time_ut": 1661323204,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0dc3\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dc0 \u0db4\u0dcf\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u0dd2\u0d9a \u0db4\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0db1\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d87\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0dc0\u0dd3\u0db8\u0dda \u0d89\u0da9 \u0d9a\u0da9 \u0d85\u0dc0\u0db8\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "There is little chance of an all-party rule",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The leader of the National Freedom Front Mr. Wimal Weerawansa says that the possibility of an all-party government or all-party rule is minimal.",
        "The MP said this while speaking to the media after a discussion held by the independent parties.",
        "The MP said that looking at the state of the country, the political parties do not have a broad enough mind to join together and make a commitment to build the country and the president also has no desire and no program for it."
      ],
      "title_ents": [],
